          </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
            <p class="para">Ezen kívül az <a href="http://pragprog.com/titles/rails3/agile-web-development-with-rails-third-edition" class="ulink" title="http://pragprog.com/titles/rails3/agile-web-development-with-rails-third-edition">Agile Development with Rails</a> könyv is nagyszerű információforrás.</p>
          </li>
